  <description type="morphology">Plants (3–)5–8(–10) cm. Secondary stem leaves 2–3.5 × 1.4 mm. Branch leaves ovate, 1.5–2 × 0.5–0.6 mm; margins coarsely serrate at apex; apex acute to acuminate; basal laminal cells 6–10 × 1–2 µm; medial juxtacostal cells short-rhomboidal, longest axis 45° to costa, 3–5 × 1–2 µm; apical cells elongate-rhombic, 3–5 × 1–2 µm. Sexual condition synoicous or autoicous.</description>
